                     <interp inst="t17840915-104-verdict502" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY, 39 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>To be <rs id="t17840915-104-punish503" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-104-punish503" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
